            "image": "https://www.vaticannews.va/content/dam/vaticannews/santi/20200427_Wikimedia-Commons_Menologio-di-Basilio-II_985_SIMEONE-VESCOVO-DI-GERUSALEMME.jpg/_jcr_content/renditions/cq5dam.thumbnail.cropped.1500.844.jpeg",
