            "image": "https://www.vaticannews.va/content/dam/vaticannews/santi/20200520_Wikimedia-Commons_NUNZIO-SULPRIZIO.jpg/_jcr_content/renditions/cq5dam.thumbnail.cropped.1500.844.jpeg",
