            "image": "https://www.vaticannews.va/content/dam/vaticannews/santi/20191011_Basilica-di-san-Paolo-fuori-le-mura_medaglioni-papi_GIOVANNI-PAOLO-II.jpg/_jcr_content/renditions/cq5dam.thumbnail.cropped.1500.844.jpeg",
